    <section id="resume-tips">
        <h2>Resume Writing Tips</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Keep your resume clear and concise (1-2 pages).</li>
            <li>Use a professional email address.</li>
            <li>Include a summary at the top, highlighting your key strengths.</li>
            <li>Focus on quantifiable achievements.</li>
            <li>Tailor your resume to the job description.</li>
            <li>Use action verbs and avoid buzzwords.</li>
            <li>Ensure proper formatting for readability.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="career-questions">
        <h2>Common Career Questions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>What are your career goals?</li>
            <li>What motivates you to succeed?</li>
            <li>Where do you see yourself in 5 years?</li>
            <li>What skills do you want to develop?</li>
            <li>What’s your work style?</li>
            <li>Why did you choose this field?</li>
            <li>What are your biggest strengths and weaknesses?</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

