    <section id="interview-questions">
        <h2>Common Interview Questions and Answers</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tell me about yourself?</strong><br>
                <em>Answer Tip:</em> Keep it short and professional. Mention your background, skills, and career goals.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Why do you want to work here?</strong><br>
                <em>Answer Tip:</em> Show that you’ve researched the company and align your values with theirs.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Why should we hire you?</strong><br>
                <em>Answer Tip:</em> Highlight your unique skills and how they fit the job requirements.
            </li>
            <li><strong>What’s your biggest strength?</strong><br>
                <em>Answer Tip:</em> Provide examples of how your strengths have helped in previous roles.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Tell me about a challenge you've faced and how you overcame it?</strong><br>
                <em>Answer Tip:</em> Show problem-solving skills and how you handle adversity.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

